---
alwaysApply: true
---

- When told to work on doc/test, never implement code 
  unless explicitly told to do so.
- This repository use unittest for testing. when testing, 
  make sure the working directory is the parent 
  directory of the repository.
- This environment use .venv for virtual environment.
- `.cursor/temp` contains temporary files for context, 
  assume they will not be available in the future.
